headline: GTA Online
subtitle: On the Podium this Week: Annis RE-7B
content:
While you may be helping or hindering the financial success of The Diamond Casino & Resort (or just visiting the bar), there’s no downside to spinning the Lucky Wheel: there’s GTA$, RP, clothing, mystery prizes, and more, all up for grabs at no cost to you.

This week’s top prize on the podium is the Annis RE-7B, a Japanese-built racing prototype designed with the most exacting specifications and race conditions in mind.
